instantly.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Smart item search \u2014 now you can search not only by name but also by game name (for example, &#8220;Dota 2&#8221; will show all available elements from there).<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Support for instant application \u2013 any purchased elements can be applied in 1 click without going into Steam settings.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>What has improved:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> After the first release of customization in 2.3.0, SIH received a lot of user feedback, and the developers responded promptly:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Completely redesigned the customization section.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improved search, filtering, and visual display of elements.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Updated customization information \u2013 added new backgrounds, animations, avatars, etc.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Simplified disabling and resetting customization in one click.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now it&#8217;s not just a &#8220;cool feature,&#8221; but a full-fledged customization tool that works quickly, conveniently, and flexibly.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0041575 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0041575\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-218b435 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"218b435\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=