ctive overlay that explains how to use the new features. This makes SIH even more friendly to beginners and convenient for experienced users.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ddc5b6c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ddc5b6c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbe9324 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bbe9324\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Trading: Sales Have Become Simpler and Faster<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77c7249 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"77c7249\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One area that is constantly improving is trading and inventory management.<\/span><\/p><p><b>New features:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quick sale of items on SIH.app directly from the Steam inventory.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ability to sell a group of items in a couple of clicks.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixes and improvements to market integration: fixed issues with currencies, button display (&#8220;Inspect in game&#8221;, &#8220;Instant sell&#8221;), and frequent errors when loading items.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">New behavior when relisting items in Steam \u2013 now adapted to the latest platform changes.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Additionally, you can now use items directly from SIH \u2013 for example, a previously purchased profile background can be applied to your account immediately, bypassing lengthy visits to Steam settings and menus.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9cae9d0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9cae9d0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ef6b66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0ef6b66\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Free Items and Sales<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-87f6bc5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"87f6bc5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2375\" alt=\"Free Items and Sales\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon-650x366.webp 650w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/213_11zon.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a2d296 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0a2d296\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During the Steam Spring Sale, a special button for automatically collecting free items appeared in SIH. An information window has also been added showing which items were received through SIH.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is a great aid for those who want to grab freebies without spending time on it \u2013 SIH will do everything for you.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74e0dee e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"74e0dee\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e98d009 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e98d009\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Under-the-Hood Improvements<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3858e19 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3858e19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Over dozens of minor versions (from 2.3.1 to 2.3.9 and beyond), developers focused on optimization, bug fixes, and increasing stability:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Accelerated loading of float values.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixed errors with mass adding games to cart.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixed bugs with the display of buttons and pages in the Steam interface.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Updated integration with DMarket.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Added support for the new Avan.Market marketplace in the price comparison block.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a646ea2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a646ea2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-833a672 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"833a672\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Technical Improvements and Redesign<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb6d7a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"eb6d7a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2378\" alt=\"Technical Improvements and Redesign\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2-650x366.webp 650w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/11_11zon-2.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1484416 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1484416\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Among other changes:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mass badge crafting \u2013 if you&#8217;ve accumulated many card sets, now you can craft them all at once.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improved interface on the friends page: now you can see the date when the friendship began, as well as the trading history with this user.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">New option \u2014 disabling the visual display of transaction history if you want to maintain privacy.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ability to locally reset SDA files if authorization problems occur.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c9d877 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7c9d877\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-faf063d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"faf063d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CSFloat Integration<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0dfd13e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0dfd13e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the release of 2.4.1, SIH received integration with CSFloat, making it even more convenient for traders and skin collectors. Now float values can be viewed, checked, and analyzed directly through SIH.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef24110 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ef24110\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1945f19 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1945f19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Update?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da789ea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"da789ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Steam Inventory Helper is not just an extension, but a real assistant for gamers and traders. With each update, it becomes faster, more functional, and closer to your needs. Want a stylish profile? Customize it in two clicks. Need fast trading? Use new marketplaces and instant selling. Collecting badges? Craft them in bulk!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The latest version 2.4.1 is already available for download. Install the update and discover how SIH turns Steam into an even more convenient and exciting platform. Your ideas and wishes are always taken into account \u2013 join the community and share your impressions!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Steam Inventory Helper (SIH) continues to improve, offering Steam users new capabilities for inventory management, profile customization, and simplified trading. With updates [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2376,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[27],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2374","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-devlog"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>SIH 2.4.1: Steam Personalization, Smart Trading, and CSFloat Integration \u2014 What&#039;s New in the Extension? - Sih.app blog<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"The new SIH 2.4.1 changes the game: five major updates every Steam user should know about.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/devlog\/sih-2-4-1-steam-personalization-smart-trading-and-csfloat-integration-whats-new-in-the-extension\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"SIH 2.4.1: Steam Personalization, Smart Trading, and CSFloat Inte